|-
|  Bank 02  ||  $8000-$BFFF  ||  $08010-$0C010  ||  Text compression, dialog data
|-
|  Bank 03  ||  $C000-$FFFF  ||  $0C010-$10010  ||  Fixed bank, core gameplay systems
|}

